response.original_title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!: The Wubb Club
response.overview: Everybody's favorite bendy-tailed buddy and his friends invite you to join Wuzzleburgs most fun club ever! In these seven popular episodes, Wubbzy, Widget and Walden build a crazy clubhouse, meet their new neighbor Daizy, and start a band called the Wuzzles! Your club membership entitles you to laughter and learning along with slippy-slide floors, rubber bouncy rooms and flower-shaped houses! All of this and more is waiting for you in THE WUBB CLUB!
response.title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!: The Wubb Club
